"title": "5874: happiness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5874",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A state of pleasure or joy experienced both by people and by God, but subject to change according to circumstances. True happiness derives from a secure and settled knowledge of God and a rejoicing in his works and covenant faithfulness. God rejoices over his faithful people.</p>\n<h2>Happiness found in human relationships</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:5\">DEU 24:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:13\">GEN 30:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:19\">GEN 34:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:8\">1KI 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps113:9\">PSA 113:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:24\">PRO 23:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:9\">ECC 9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:10\">SNG 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:24\">ROM 15:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:13\">2CO 7:13</a></p>\n<h2>Happiness found in people and things</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:20\">1KI 4:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:14\">LUK 1:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut20:61\">DEU 20:61</a>SA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:3\">18:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:17\">1SA 20:17</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:3-Ps127:5\">PSA 127:3–127:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:12\">ECC 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:19\">ECC 5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:15\">ECC 8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:9\">ECC 11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:22\">ISA 65:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:6\">JON 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:19\">LUK 12:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:21\">JHN 16:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:25-Phil2:30\">PHP 2:25–2:30</a></p>\n<h2>Happiness found in God</h2>\n<h3>In God's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:11\">PSA 16:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:6\">PSA 21:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:4\">PSA 43:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:9\">1TH 3:9</a></p>\n<h3>In God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:35\">PSA 119:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:2\">ISA 55:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:16\">JER 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:37\">MRK 12:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:22\">ROM 7:22</a></p>\n<h3>In God's actions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:6\">GEN 21:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:23\">ACT 11:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:9\">EXO 18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:1\">1SA 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:5\">1SA 19:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:66\">1KI 8:66</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:16\">EST 8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:6\">PSA 16:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:4\">PSA 92:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:2\">PSA 111:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:10\">ISA 61:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:48\">ACT 13:48</a></p>\n<h2>God's happiness</h2>\n<h3>In obedient people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:9-Deut30:10\">DEU 30:9–30:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:22\">1SA 15:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:11\">PSA 147:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:17\">ISA 9:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:21\">MAT 25:21</a></p>\n<h3>In the righteous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:20\">PRO 11:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:11\">PSA 147:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:1\">PRO 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:26\">ECC 2:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:24\">JER 9:24</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's recipe for happiness</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:3-Matt5:10\">MAT 5:3–5:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:20-Luke6:22\">LUK 6:20–6:22</a></p>\n<h2>Happiness may not be permanent</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:14\">ECC 7:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:9\">EST 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:7\">JOB 7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:6\">PSA 10:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:13\">PRO 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:9\">ECC 11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:9\">JER 16:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:15\">LAM 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:12\">JOL 1:12</a></p>\n<h2>Happiness for those who trust in God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:12\">PSA 84:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:12\">PSA 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:8\">PSA 34:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:4\">PSA 40:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:5\">PSA 146:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:20\">PRO 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:7\">JER 17:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:45\">LUK 1:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:29\">JHN 20:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:9\">GAL 3:9</a></p>\n<h2>Happiness for those who obey God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:15\">PSA 89:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:17\">JOB 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:1-Ps1:2\">PSA 1:1–1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:12\">PSA 94:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:1\">PSA 112:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps128:1\">PSA 128:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:14\">PRO 28:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:18\">PRO 29:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:1-Isa56:2\">ISA 56:1–56:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:27-Luke11:28\">LUK 11:27–11:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:3\">REV 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:7\">REV 22:7</a></p>\n<h2>Happiness for those who are forgiven</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:1-Ps32:2\">PSA 32:1–32:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:7-Rom4:8\">ROM 4:7–4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:14\">REV 22:14</a></p>\n<h2>Happiness for those who suffer persecution</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:14\">1PE 3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:11-Matt5:12\">MAT 5:11–5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:14\">1PE 4:14</a></p>\n<h2>Happiness for those who persevere</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:6\">MAT 11:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:12\">JAS 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:11\">JAS 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:15\">REV 16:15</a></p>",
